{
  "stem": "21626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And to my amazement the president not only remembered me, but remembered the words I put on my card to him and introduced me to his wife saying, this young lady sent me a lovely little letter last Christmas.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he asked me to stay with him for the rest of the program.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he told-- asked me if I was happy, if was looked after properly, and, and what I missed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said to him, well, of course, my parents most of all, and being in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But otherwise, I do miss not having Czech education, and particularly as I didn't get into a grammar school, not because of my English, but I couldn't master the maths in, in a month and a half, which, after which I had to take my 11 Plus.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I told him how I missed not being in a Czech school and not having Czech children to play with and me and my friends, he said, but I can change all that.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there is a school here in Britain just for such children as you are.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I tell you what, I'll arrange it myself through my office.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I walked home on stars that night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- my feet never touched the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I kept talking to the stars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I kept saying to them, Mommy, Daddy, I hope you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hope you are aware of this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If only I could write.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If only I could shout and tell you that I'm going, actually, to a Czech school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Rainford or Daddy Rainford was pleased for me, but a little bit sad that they'd be losing me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, but you won't be losing me, because I'm going to come back every holiday.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
